 * Animated Counter Polyfill
 * 
 * Animates numbers from 0 to their target value when they scroll into view.
 * Targets elements with [data-nce-counter].
 * 
 * Algorithm:
 * 1. Find all target elements.
 * 2. Parse the target integer from their innerText.
 * 3. Use IntersectionObserver to trigger animation.
 * 4. Animate innerText from 0 -> target using requestAnimationFrame.
 */
